name: Artist: 森倉円 | Morikuraen artist's painting style
description:
森倉円 Style LoRA

中文 | English

仿森倉円的作画风格的LoRA模型。

权重建议值：1 (or 0.5~1.4)

基于模型：Anything-5RE

训练信息：筛选出共计540张原画（含裁剪图），迭代1080步，多分辨率智能定向训练。

其他的一些建议：EasyNegative。此外，万一畸形四肢换个种子重画就行。

The LoRA model imitates the painting style of Morikuraen.

Recommended weight value: 1 (or 0.5-1.4)

Based on model: Anything-5RE

Training information: A total of 540 original images (including cropped images) were selected for 1080 iterations of multi-resolution intelligent targeted training.

Other suggestions: Use EasyNegative. Additionally, if there are any abnormal limbs, try redrawing them with a different seed.
